Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,くっつけポポ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,黏回去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,くっつけポポ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:20.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,黏回去吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,みんなが心配してるデス
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,大家都很擔心你們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,早く帰ったほうがいいデス
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.07,0:10:29.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們還是儘早回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.05,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あの子が戻ってくるんだなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.05,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那孩子回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.47,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.47,Default CN,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,自動車  ベッドの上に  置いてないよ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:40.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我明明沒有把車子放到床上啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,おかしいなぁ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,真奇怪...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:45.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,今  電話があって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:47.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,爸爸來電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,パパが  もうすぐ駅に着くって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,說馬上就到車站了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,迎えに行くから  早く支度しなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:51.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你快準備一下 我們一起去接他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どうしよう...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:54.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,えっ？さっきまでこの家にいたの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.62,0:11:05.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,欸？剛才還在這房子裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,そうデス
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:06.48,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どこへ行ったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:06.48,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那孩子現在去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.42,Default JP,,0,0,0,,それは分からないんだなぁ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.42,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這我們就不知道了...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.02,Default JP,,0,0,0,,何だか嫌な予感がするメポ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.17,0:11:11.02,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我有不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,早くさがすメポ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,快去找他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,急ぐデス
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.77,0:11:13.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,趕緊了趕緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.17,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:16.17,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保倫...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.22,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ルルン...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:17.22,Default CN,,0,0,0,,露露...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.62,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.62,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}元気だすポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你要振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:57.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,誰...？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:57.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是誰...？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,望はパパが大好きポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,望你是最喜歡爸爸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,パパも  望が大好きポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:05.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你的爸爸也是最喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ここでジッとしてたら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你要是一直躲在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.87,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}パパに会えないポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.87,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}就見不到爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,でも...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:12.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ずっと  ずっと会えないポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:13.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}會永遠 永遠都見不到的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:14.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,いや！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.32,0:12:14.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.75,Default JP,,0,0,0,,勇気を出すポポ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:16.75,Default CN,,0,0,0,,那就鼓起勇氣來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,頑張るポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,頑張るルル
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.35,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:36.35,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}頑張るポポ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:38.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}你要加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,頑張るルル！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.48,Default JP,,0,0,0,,このあたりだと思うんだなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.48,Default CN,,0,0,0,,應該就是在這邊了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:49.85,Default JP,,0,0,0,,近いデス
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.90,0:12:49.85,Default CN,,0,0,0,,就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,このあたりに  いる気配が...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,這附近有他們的氣息...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}お前達
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:52.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.70,Default JP,,0,0,0,,あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:53.70,Default CN,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.25,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お前達がいると  いうことは...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.25,Default CN,,0,0,0,,既然你們會在這裡 那也就是說...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.52,Default JP,,0,0,0,,この近くに...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:00.52,Default CN,,0,0,0,,在這附近有...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ルルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:12.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,露露！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.65,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ポルン！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.65,Default CN,,0,0,0,,保倫！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.10,Default JP,,0,0,0,,お前達  プリキュアはどこだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.45,0:13:23.10,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們快老實交代 Precure在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.82,Default JP,,0,0,0,,言わなければ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:25.82,Default CN,,0,0,0,,不說的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.90,Default JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8}待ちなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.90,Default CN,,0,0,0,,{\an8}慢著！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ひかり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.37,Default JP,,0,0,0,,またあなたなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.37,Default CN,,0,0,0,,又是你？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.00,Default JP,,0,0,0,,やはり出てきたか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.00,Default CN,,0,0,0,,你們果然現身了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:37.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,まとめて叩き潰してやる
